{"id":609923,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/05/法立方ai-历史上的劳动节，就是为了对抗996/","date":"2019-05-01T16:21:17Z","modified":"2019-05-01T16:46:12Z","title":"法立方AI | 历史上的劳动节，就是为了对抗996","content":"<p>原创： 王若翰    来源：法立方AI</p>\n<p>《立方说法》是法立方推出的真人律师面对面访谈系列漫画。漫画中的每一位律师，都是现实中活生生的律政男神或女神哦！</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609928\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/1-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/1-1.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/1-1-300x264.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/1-1-768x675.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609929\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/2-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"371\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/2-2.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/2-2-300x222.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/2-2-768x569.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p>为了刺激经济的高速发展，榨取更多的剩余价值，资本家不断采取增加劳动时间和劳动强度的办法来残酷地剥削工人。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609930\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/3-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"773\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/3-1.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/3-1-194x300.png 194w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/3-1-768x1187.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/3-1-663x1024.png 663w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609931\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/4-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"957\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/4-1.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/4-1-157x300.png 157w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/4-1-768x1470.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/4-1-535x1024.png 535w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609933\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/5-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"625\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/5-1.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/5-1-240x300.png 240w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/5-1-768x960.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609934\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"791\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/7.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/7-190x300.png 190w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/7-768x1214.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/7-648x1024.png 648w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>但是，某些资本家根本不予理睬，仍旧知法犯法，视法律为无物。这一点上，古今中外似乎高度一致！</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609937\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"717\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/8.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/8-209x300.png 209w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/8-768x1101.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/8-714x1024.png 714w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609938\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1250\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/9.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/9-120x300.png 120w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/9-768x1920.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/9-410x1024.png 410w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609945\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1250\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/10.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/10-120x300.png 120w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/10-768x1920.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/10-410x1024.png 410w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609946\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"602\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/11.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/11-249x300.png 249w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/11-768x925.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609948\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/untitled.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/untitled.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/untitled-300x188.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/untitled-768x480.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609947\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/13.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"361\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/13.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/13-300x217.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/13-768x555.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>即便是不定时工作制，也不能成为996工作制的法律依据：不定时工作制是指企业因工作情况特殊，需要安排职工机动作业，无法实行标准工时制度，采用不确定工作时间的工时制度。在不定时工作制下，除法定节假日外，员工加班企业无需支付加班工资。</p>\n<p>注释：</p>\n<p>996工作制是指工作日早9点上班，晚上9点下班，中午和傍晚休息1小时（或不到），总计10小时以上，并且一周工作6天的工作制度。</p>\n<p>比之更甚的还有某东哥提出的“8116+8”工作制，指周一到周六6天，从早8点工作到晚11点再加上周日工作8个小时。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609949\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/14.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"846\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/14.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/14-177x300.png 177w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/14-768x1299.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/14-605x1024.png 605w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>进入公众号，点击如下位置留言</p>\n<p>如果你有想了解的法律问题，请通过法立方主页面留言。考虑到部分问题可能涉及个人隐私，因此大家的留言仅后台专业法律人员可见，不会出现在每篇文章下部的公示页面。同时，也欢迎各位愿意帮助读者答疑解惑的律政达人们主动与我们联系。</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"st-related-posts\">\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2019.04.20</span> <a title=\"沉默的河 | 北漂996青年梦想消亡史\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/04/%e6%b2%89%e9%bb%98%e7%9a%84%e6%b2%b3-%e5%8c%97%e6%bc%82996%e9%9d%92%e5%b9%b4%e6%a2%a6%e6%83%b3%e6%b6%88%e4%ba%a1%e5%8f%b2/\">沉默的河 | 北漂996青年梦想消亡史</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2019.04.18</span> <a title=\"干货 | 为什么马云刘强东这次有些怂？\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/04/%e5%b9%b2%e8%b4%a7-%e4%b8%ba%e4%bb%80%e4%b9%88%e9%a9%ac%e4%ba%91%e5%88%98%e5%bc%ba%e4%b8%9c%e8%bf%99%e6%ac%a1%e6%9c%89%e4%ba%9b%e6%80%82%ef%bc%9f/\">干货 | 为什么马云刘强东这次有些怂？</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2019.04.16</span> <a title=\"阿柴 | 大逃杀时代：温水正接近沸腾\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/04/%e9%98%bf%e6%9f%b4-%e5%a4%a7%e9%80%83%e6%9d%80%e6%97%b6%e4%bb%a3%ef%bc%9a%e6%b8%a9%e6%b0%b4%e6%ad%a3%e6%8e%a5%e8%bf%91%e6%b2%b8%e8%85%be/\">阿柴 | 大逃杀时代：温水正接近沸腾</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2019.04.05</span> <a title=\"BBC |中国程序员GitHub上抗议“996”血汗加班走红网络\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/04/bbc-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e7%a8%8b%e5%ba%8f%e5%91%98github%e4%b8%8a%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae996%e8%a1%80%e6%b1%97%e5%8a%a0%e7%8f%ad%e8%b5%b0%e7%ba%a2%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c/\">BBC |中国程序员GitHub上抗议“996”血汗加班走红网络</a></li>\n</ul>\n","author":970,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,23855],"tags":[38339,10983,10778]}